On the bright side , <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> has scored a few points of its own in this diplomatic tug of war .
When <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Chen</ENAMEX> arrived in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Costa Rica</ENAMEX> on the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">18th</ENAMEX> , his hosts departed from the pattern of <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">the past few years</ENAMEX> by promising to support the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">ROC</ENAMEX> s bid for membership in <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">the United Nations</ENAMEX> .
