<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Chen Shui - bian</ENAMEX> is the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">first</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">ROC</ENAMEX> president ever to travel to <ENAMEX TYPE="LOC">western Africa</ENAMEX> .
