President <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Chen</ENAMEX> received a very warm welcome in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Nicaragua</ENAMEX> , but the local press still mentioned " checkbook diplomacy " in reporting on the visit .
The <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">ROC</ENAMEX> 's ambassador to <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Nicaragua</ENAMEX> , <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Antonio Tsai</ENAMEX> , bluntly argued in a briefing with <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Chen</ENAMEX> that <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Taiwan</ENAMEX> 's foreign assistance to <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Nicaragua</ENAMEX> was being misused .
